{"tid":1224813,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖) 有冇人心口/背脊生暗瘡之後起咗呢啲野？","createTime":"2019-06-15T05:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T15:48:44.000Z","uid":194299,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b82573fca9304a6cc55256f5b6985ef695b421ff","tid":1224813,"uid":194299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMvD3W9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMvD3W9.jpg&h=030d9aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似一粒粒雞皮咁，可以點解決？去過醫院做磨皮都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ffdd04983ecf2613b7a795d0713c1843b7015d","tid":1224813,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:07:42.000Z","msg":"問： 手淫跟長痘痘有關系嗎?<br />\n<br />\n答：有關系,那是因為手淫刺激後雄性激素分泌得更多了. 所以和長痘痘是有聯系的.<br />\n<br />\n答：痤瘡也被稱為暗瘡或者青春痘、粉刺，它是青少年時期最常見的炎性皮膚病，對於生了痤瘡的人來說，只要積極尋找發病的透因，並進行合理的治療，消退皮疹並不困難，重要的是在治療前後采取必要的皮膚護理，預防加重和反復遷延復發。痤瘡的發病原因較多，也較復雜。主要有外在因素和內在因素二類。"},{"pid":"621caa70e0548e32d0e34b5c94a926f0b5119726","tid":1224813,"uid":129011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82573fca9304a6cc55256f5b6985ef695b421ff","tid":1224813,"uid":194299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMvD3W9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMvD3W9.jpg&h=030d9aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似一粒粒雞皮咁，可以點解決？去過醫院做磨皮都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:10:56.000Z","msg":"石頭瘡？"},{"pid":"75324b0d0d2d421b721f2b5b69334228ac775356","tid":1224813,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:13:57.000Z","msg":"影低少少睇下"},{"pid":"440b7f4360055ebfe666d03a740b42cd35f052e7","tid":1224813,"uid":194299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"621caa70e0548e32d0e34b5c94a926f0b5119726","tid":1224813,"uid":12